    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait 5000 units of B12? is that like a lot? and i'm not sure if i should take the ibuprofen with my migraine meds or if that's bad. do you think the eye thing is actually serious or can it just be part of the migraine aura? i'd rather not go to the ER if i don't have to, it's so expensive and the wait is always terrible.",
