      "content": "okay so i'll try the warm cloth and the tylenol. but just to be sure, if i start feeling numb in my arm or if the drooping gets worse, should i still just stay home and wait for the meds to kick in? i'm really hoping i can just sleep this off so i don't have to deal with the hospital.",
